00:02:53.486 --> 00:02:55.156 A:middle
First, displaying web content.

00:02:55.946 --> 00:02:56.956 A:middle
There are a couple of different

00:02:56.956 --> 00:02:58.366 A:middle
ways, but today I'm going to

00:02:58.366 --> 00:03:00.236 A:middle
talk about two of those, using

00:02:58.366 --> 00:03:00.236 A:middle
talk about two of those, using

