SFSafariViewController and using

00:03:02.036 --> 00:03:02.966 A:middle
WKWebView.

00:03:04.216 --> 00:03:05.736 A:middle
To start off, let's talk about

00:03:05.736 --> 00:03:07.176 A:middle
SFSafariViewController.

00:03:08.416 --> 00:03:10.096 A:middle
If you don't know where your

00:03:10.096 --> 00:03:12.446 A:middle
user will be going on the web,

00:03:12.596 --> 00:03:14.196 A:middle
Safari View Controller is really

00:03:14.196 --> 00:03:15.516 A:middle
a good thing for you to use.

00:03:16.286 --> 00:03:17.706 A:middle
It gives you standard browsing

00:03:17.706 --> 00:03:19.196 A:middle
features so you don't need to

00:03:19.196 --> 00:03:20.586 A:middle
worry about implementing an

00:03:20.616 --> 00:03:21.666 A:middle
in-app web browser.

00:03:22.866 --> 00:03:24.086 A:middle
With just a couple lines of

00:03:24.226 --> 00:03:25.876 A:middle
code, you get an in-app web

00:03:25.876 --> 00:03:27.306 A:middle
browser with all of the features

00:03:27.306 --> 00:03:28.646 A:middle
that your users know and love

00:03:28.686 --> 00:03:30.636 A:middle
from Safari in your app.

00:03:32.206 --> 00:03:33.816 A:middle
Safari View Controller is also

00:03:33.816 --> 00:03:34.926 A:middle
great for getting users

00:03:34.926 --> 00:03:36.516 A:middle
authenticated to a third-party

00:03:36.576 --> 00:03:36.856 A:middle
service.

00:03:38.016 --> 00:03:39.676 A:middle
It has the security that users

00:03:39.676 --> 00:03:41.636 A:middle
need while logging in and it has

00:03:41.766 --> 00:03:43.126 A:middle
features that can help them get

00:03:43.126 --> 00:03:44.046 A:middle
logged in quickly.

00:03:44.736 --> 00:03:46.326 A:middle
One main example is Password

00:03:46.326 --> 00:03:47.016 A:middle
AutoFill.

00:03:47.376 --> 00:03:48.496 A:middle
They can quickly fill their

00:03:48.496 --> 00:03:50.446 A:middle
saved passwords from Safari and

00:03:50.446 --> 00:03:51.986 A:middle
log in with a tap of a button.

00:03:54.946 --> 00:03:57.136 A:middle
Now let's talk about WKWebView.

00:03:57.916 --> 00:03:59.566 A:middle
If you don't know the web, or if

00:03:59.566 --> 00:04:00.836 A:middle
you know the content that you'll

00:03:59.566 --> 00:04:00.836 A:middle
you know the content that you'll

00:04:00.836 --> 00:04:02.666 A:middle
be displaying to users ahead of

00:04:02.666 --> 00:04:04.296 A:middle
time, or you even have control

00:04:04.296 --> 00:04:06.556 A:middle
over the web content, WKWebView

00:04:06.556 --> 00:04:07.626 A:middle
might be right for you.

00:04:08.386 --> 00:04:09.806 A:middle
It allows you to manipulate the

00:04:09.806 --> 00:04:11.566 A:middle
DOM using Javascript.

00:04:12.386 --> 00:04:13.676 A:middle
You can also customize

00:04:13.676 --> 00:04:15.766 A:middle
navigations by blocking or

00:04:15.766 --> 00:04:16.706 A:middle
modifying them.

00:04:18.196 --> 00:04:19.846 A:middle
It's a view of web content, so

00:04:19.846 --> 00:04:21.396 A:middle
you can add your own native UI

00:04:21.676 --> 00:04:22.796 A:middle
around the web content.

00:04:23.386 --> 00:04:25.126 A:middle
This is great if part of your

00:04:25.126 --> 00:04:26.646 A:middle
app's UI is implemented using

00:04:26.646 --> 00:04:27.676 A:middle
web technologies.

00:04:28.816 --> 00:04:30.176 A:middle
The web content can blend

00:04:30.296 --> 00:04:31.636 A:middle
seamlessly in with your app's

00:04:31.636 --> 00:04:33.626 A:middle
native UI, so users don't even

00:04:33.626 --> 00:04:35.076 A:middle
need to know that they're

00:04:35.076 --> 00:04:36.386 A:middle
interacting with web content.

00:04:38.466 --> 00:04:39.716 A:middle
But let's get back to Safari

00:04:39.716 --> 00:04:40.836 A:middle
View Controller since I think

00:04:40.836 --> 00:04:41.746 A:middle
that's why you're all here.

00:04:44.136 --> 00:04:45.266 A:middle
Safari View Controller makes

00:04:45.266 --> 00:04:46.616 A:middle
in-app web browsing easy.

00:04:46.686 --> 00:04:48.156 A:middle
As I mentioned before, with just

00:04:48.156 --> 00:04:49.796 A:middle
a couple lines of code, you've

00:04:49.796 --> 00:04:51.566 A:middle
got a fully featured web browser

00:04:51.566 --> 00:04:54.866 A:middle
within your app.

00:04:54.866 --> 00:04:56.496 A:middle
It provides a secure and safe

00:04:56.566 --> 00:04:58.236 A:middle
browsing experience for users.

00:04:59.236 --> 00:05:00.636 A:middle
Let me tell you about a few of

00:04:59.236 --> 00:05:00.636 A:middle
Let me tell you about a few of

00:05:00.636 --> 00:05:02.286 A:middle
the security features you get

00:05:02.286 --> 00:05:03.516 A:middle
with Safari View Controller.

00:05:04.936 --> 00:05:06.726 A:middle
First, process separation.

00:05:07.426 --> 00:05:08.786 A:middle
There's your app's content and

00:05:08.786 --> 00:05:09.776 A:middle
then there's web content.

00:05:10.826 --> 00:05:12.296 A:middle
Safari View Controller is in a

00:05:12.406 --> 00:05:14.376 A:middle
separate process from your app.

00:05:14.896 --> 00:05:16.876 A:middle
This means that anything that

00:05:16.876 --> 00:05:18.966 A:middle
the user does on the web won't

00:05:18.966 --> 00:05:20.256 A:middle
have an effect on your app's

00:05:20.346 --> 00:05:20.706 A:middle
content.

00:05:21.436 --> 00:05:23.636 A:middle
If they browse to malicious web

00:05:23.676 --> 00:05:25.566 A:middle
page it won't be able to affect

00:05:25.626 --> 00:05:26.386 A:middle
your app's data.

00:05:27.256 --> 00:05:28.416 A:middle
You get out of the business of

00:05:28.416 --> 00:05:30.226 A:middle
taking care of user security on

00:05:30.226 --> 00:05:31.896 A:middle
the web because Safari View

00:05:31.896 --> 00:05:33.296 A:middle
Controller will take care of

00:05:33.296 --> 00:05:34.016 A:middle
that for you.

00:05:34.886 --> 00:05:36.526 A:middle
It provides critical security

00:05:36.556 --> 00:05:37.056 A:middle
features.

00:05:37.266 --> 00:05:39.216 A:middle
Let's talk about a couple of

00:05:39.296 --> 00:05:39.386 A:middle
those.

00:05:41.576 --> 00:05:43.256 A:middle
The lock icon here indicates to

00:05:43.256 --> 00:05:44.346 A:middle
the user that they're browsing

00:05:44.346 --> 00:05:45.686 A:middle
over a secure connection.

00:05:46.126 --> 00:05:47.336 A:middle
This is a really important

00:05:47.386 --> 00:05:48.606 A:middle
feature in a browser.

00:05:49.156 --> 00:05:50.096 A:middle
And you don't need to worry

00:05:50.096 --> 00:05:51.446 A:middle
about implementing it if you use

00:05:51.446 --> 00:05:52.826 A:middle
Safari View Controller for your

00:05:52.826 --> 00:05:53.866 A:middle
in-app web browser.

00:05:55.286 --> 00:05:57.136 A:middle
Safari View Controller will also

00:05:57.136 --> 00:05:58.576 A:middle
warn users if they might be

00:05:58.576 --> 00:06:00.156 A:middle
trying to navigate to a page

00:05:58.576 --> 00:06:00.156 A:middle
trying to navigate to a page

00:06:00.156 --> 00:06:01.376 A:middle
that's going to try to steal

00:06:01.376 --> 00:06:02.316 A:middle
their information.

00:06:02.986 --> 00:06:04.546 A:middle
This page is trying to imitate

00:06:04.546 --> 00:06:06.346 A:middle
example.com to get my

00:06:06.416 --> 00:06:07.036 A:middle
information.

00:06:07.036 --> 00:06:09.646 A:middle
And you get features from

00:06:09.646 --> 00:06:10.236 A:middle
Safari.

00:06:10.506 --> 00:06:11.996 A:middle
Let me just highlight a few of

00:06:11.996 --> 00:06:13.136 A:middle
the features that you'll get

00:06:13.256 --> 00:06:14.526 A:middle
with Safari View Controller.

00:06:15.546 --> 00:06:17.766 A:middle
You get AutoFill of passwords,

00:06:17.766 --> 00:06:19.456 A:middle
contact info, and credit cards.

00:06:20.096 --> 00:06:21.946 A:middle
Users can quickly fill out forms

00:06:21.946 --> 00:06:22.536 A:middle
on the web.

00:06:24.546 --> 00:06:26.506 A:middle
Reader is an awesome feature for

00:06:26.506 --> 00:06:27.806 A:middle
decluttering articles on the

00:06:27.806 --> 00:06:28.136 A:middle
web.

00:06:28.626 --> 00:06:30.166 A:middle
Our users of this feature love

00:06:30.166 --> 00:06:31.536 A:middle
it, and they'll love getting to

00:06:31.536 --> 00:06:32.616 A:middle
use it in your app.

00:06:34.666 --> 00:06:36.246 A:middle
ApplePay on the web can help

00:06:36.246 --> 00:06:37.866 A:middle
users quickly make payments

00:06:38.186 --> 00:06:39.876 A:middle
while shopping on the web within

00:06:39.876 --> 00:06:43.156 A:middle
your app.

00:06:43.156 --> 00:06:44.446 A:middle
And users get access to the

00:06:44.446 --> 00:06:46.106 A:middle
Share Sheet that they get

00:06:46.106 --> 00:06:47.156 A:middle
elsewhere on the system.

00:06:47.676 --> 00:06:49.406 A:middle
They get access to some standard

00:06:49.466 --> 00:06:50.536 A:middle
system activities that they

00:06:50.536 --> 00:06:52.106 A:middle
might want to perform, as well

00:06:52.106 --> 00:06:53.836 A:middle
as any third-party extensions

00:06:53.936 --> 00:06:55.286 A:middle
that they have access to in

00:06:55.286 --> 00:06:55.816 A:middle
Safari.

00:06:57.866 --> 00:06:59.196 A:middle
And they get content blocker

00:06:59.196 --> 00:07:00.896 A:middle
extensions that they'd have in

00:06:59.196 --> 00:07:00.896 A:middle
extensions that they'd have in

00:07:00.946 --> 00:07:01.466 A:middle
Safari.

00:07:01.986 --> 00:07:02.846 A:middle
This means they won't be

00:07:02.846 --> 00:07:04.306 A:middle
confused about why their

00:07:04.466 --> 00:07:05.766 A:middle
ad-blocker isn't working when

00:07:05.766 --> 00:07:09.326 A:middle
browsing the web in your app.

00:07:09.326 --> 00:07:10.546 A:middle
And there are so many other

00:07:10.546 --> 00:07:12.356 A:middle
features that you get by

00:07:12.356 --> 00:07:13.476 A:middle
implementing Safari View

00:07:13.476 --> 00:07:15.306 A:middle
Controller as your in-app web

00:07:15.336 --> 00:07:15.816 A:middle
browser.

