Now, I'd like to talk to you

00:07:19.746 --> 00:07:21.146 A:middle
about how you can better match

00:07:21.146 --> 00:07:23.026 A:middle
your app's style with Safari

00:07:23.026 --> 00:07:24.676 A:middle
View Controller on iOS 11.

00:07:25.156 --> 00:07:26.486 A:middle
There are a couple of new ways.

00:07:27.846 --> 00:07:29.366 A:middle
First, it has a new look.

00:07:30.236 --> 00:07:31.556 A:middle
If you've seen Safari View

