Terms of Service and they scroll

00:25:49.486 --> 00:25:51.246 A:middle
down a little bit, the bars

00:25:51.246 --> 00:25:51.856 A:middle
collapse.

00:25:52.186 --> 00:25:53.856 A:middle
This might nice in some other

00:25:53.856 --> 00:25:55.546 A:middle
web pages, but here it could

