just get annoying.

00:25:56.786 --> 00:25:58.696 A:middle
If they want to cancel, it's two

00:25:58.696 --> 00:25:59.996 A:middle
taps away instead of one.

00:26:01.276 --> 00:26:02.626 A:middle
So, I'll show you how to improve

00:26:02.626 --> 00:26:04.176 A:middle
Safari View Controller to fit

00:26:04.176 --> 00:26:08.366 A:middle
this log in a little bit better.

00:26:08.566 --> 00:26:09.376 A:middle
Here's where I'm presenting

00:26:09.376 --> 00:26:10.466 A:middle
Safari View Controller.

00:26:11.016 --> 00:26:12.336 A:middle
Like before, it's pretty simple.

00:26:12.856 --> 00:26:15.126 A:middle
I'm creating a URL and then

00:26:15.416 --> 00:26:16.546 A:middle
passing that to Safari View

00:26:16.546 --> 00:26:17.636 A:middle
Controller's initializer.

00:26:18.946 --> 00:26:20.326 A:middle
Customizing the colors as I

00:26:20.326 --> 00:26:21.126 A:middle
showed you before.

00:26:21.706 --> 00:26:23.916 A:middle
And then presenting Safari View

00:26:23.916 --> 00:26:24.366 A:middle
Controller.

00:26:25.196 --> 00:26:27.146 A:middle
But let's make some changes.

00:26:27.306 --> 00:26:28.526 A:middle
First, let's make sure that the

00:26:28.526 --> 00:26:29.726 A:middle
bars don't collapse when they

00:26:29.726 --> 00:26:30.306 A:middle
scroll down.

00:26:34.956 --> 00:26:36.206 A:middle
So, what I've done here is

00:26:36.206 --> 00:26:37.666 A:middle
created a Safari View Controller

00:26:37.666 --> 00:26:39.826 A:middle
configuration object and then

00:26:39.826 --> 00:26:41.416 A:middle
set its barCollapsingEnabled

00:26:41.416 --> 00:26:42.536 A:middle
property to false.

00:26:42.866 --> 00:26:44.136 A:middle
This way when they scroll down

00:26:44.136 --> 00:26:45.266 A:middle
the bars won't collapse, they'll

00:26:45.266 --> 00:26:46.556 A:middle
still stay full height.

00:26:47.566 --> 00:26:49.116 A:middle
I then pass this in to Safari

00:26:49.116 --> 00:26:50.306 A:middle
View Controller's initializer.

00:26:51.796 --> 00:26:52.586 A:middle
Let's make a couple other

00:26:52.586 --> 00:26:53.296 A:middle
changes.

00:26:55.016 --> 00:26:57.056 A:middle
I've done two different things

00:26:57.056 --> 00:26:57.306 A:middle
here.

00:26:57.566 --> 00:26:58.786 A:middle
The first, is setting

00:26:58.786 --> 00:27:01.206 A:middle
dismissButtonStyle to Cancel so

00:26:58.786 --> 00:27:01.206 A:middle
dismissButtonStyle to Cancel so

